    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super reliable for me. Everything runs smoothly, and the interior is nice and clean\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks and feels great on the road. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019d love to see it go to a new home where it\u2019ll be appreciated just as much. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive!",
