    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2008 BMW M3 (E92) featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine. This naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to reach its 8,400 RPM redline. Power is managed via a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring exceptional mechanical grip through the corners. The chassis retains its precision with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and aluminum multi-link rear geometry. Recent preventative maintenance includes upgraded rod bearings and a comprehensive VANOS system inspection to ensure long-term reliability. While the exterior exhibits minor road-derived patina and stone chips consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust and the steering rack is tight and communicative. This is a mechanically sorted example of the only V8 M3 ever produced, optimized for the discerning pilot.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
