    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained vehicle that perfectly balances daily utility with premium comfort. The exterior maintains a strong curb appeal with a deep, lustrous finish, though minor stone chips on the front fascia and light surface scratches near the door handles are present upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and clean; the leather upholstery shows gentle softening and slight creasing typical of careful use, but remains free of tears. All onboard electronics, including the navigation and dual-zone climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is solid, featuring a smooth-shifting transmission and a responsive engine that has been serviced at regular intervals. It recently passed a comprehensive multi-point inspection and comes with a documented service history and two original key fobs. This is an honest, reliable car that has many miles of enjoyment left to offer.",
      "price": 31500.0,
