      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and let me tell you, it\u2019s been a total gem. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been super dependable for all my daily trips. If you're looking for a smooth ride that\u2019s been well-cared for and is ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you! I'm happy to chat if you have any questions\u2014I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
